<div class="friendbot4 js-friendbot4">
  <div class="friendbot4-step0" js-friendbot4-step="0">
    <div class="S-flex-row S-flexUtil-alignItemsCenter">
      <div class="S-flexItem-share">
        <code class="friendbot4-step0__code">curl -X POST https://horizon-testnet.payshares.org/...</code>
      </div>
      <div class="S-flexItem-noFlex">
        <button class="s-button js-friendbot4-step0__start">Start</button>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div js-friendbot4-step="1" class="friendbot4-initialHide">
    <p class="friendbot4-stepIntro">1. Use <a href="https://github.com/payshares/js-payshares-sdk">js-payshares-sdk</a> to generate the public and secret keys for your test account.</p>
    <div class="friendbot4__console">
      <div class="friendbot4__console__input">
        <code class="friendbot4__console__input__text">
          Generate Payshares testnet keys
        </code>
        <button class="s-button friendbot4__console__input__button js-friendbot4-step1-generate">
          Generate
        </button>
      </div>
      <pre class="friendbot4__console__result"><!--
      --><code class="js-friendbot4-step1-result language-javascript"></code><!--
      --></pre>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div js-friendbot4-step="2" class="friendbot4-initialHide">
    <p class="friendbot4-stepIntro">2. Using the public key you generated, ask Stroopy, our friendly robot, to send you some stakks.</p>
    <div class="friendbot4__info">
      <div class="friendbot4__bot__image">
        <img src="https://www.payshares.org/wp-content/uploads/2014/07/friendbot.png" alt="stroopy" width="54" height="70" />
      </div>
      <div class="S-flex-row">
        <input type="text" class="S-flexItem-share friendbot4__bot__input js-friendbot4__bot__input">
        <button class="s-button S-flexItem-noFlex js-friendbot4__bot__button">Get stakks</button>
      </div>
      <p class="friendbot4__bot__button__status js-friendbot4__bot__button__status"></p>
      <pre class="friendbot4__bot__button__error js-friendbot4__bot__button__error"><code class="js-friendbot4__bot__button__error__code language-javascript"></code></pre>
    </div>
    <br />
    <span class="js-friendbot4-step2-result"></span>
  </div>
  <div js-friendbot4-step="3" class="friendbot4-initialHide">
    <p class="friendbot4-stepIntro">3. Your account should contain 10,000 stakks. Run this command to view your account using the <a href="https://github.com/payshares/horizon">Horizon API</a>.
    <div class="friendbot4__console">
      <div class="friendbot4__console__input">
        <div class="friendbot4__console__input__text">
          <code class="js-friendbot4-step3-request language-shell"></code>
        </div>
        <button class="s-button friendbot4__console__input__button js-friendbot4-step3-run">
          Run command
        </button>
      </div>
      <pre class="friendbot4__console__result"><!--
      --><code class="js-friendbot4-step3-result language-javascript"></code><!--
      --></pre>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div js-friendbot4-step="4" class="friendbot4-initialHide">
    <p class="friendbot4-stepIntro">Your test account is all set! Save your keys to make other API calls on the network. </p>
    <p class="friendbot4-step4__key">
      Public key:
      <br>
      <span class="js-friendbot4-step4-address"></span>
    </p>
    <p class="friendbot4-step4__key">
      Secret key:
      <br>
      <span class="js-friendbot4-step4-seed"></span>
    </p>
    <p class="friendbot4-stepOutro">Explore more of the <a href="{{pathPrefix}}/guides/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Payshares ecosystem</a>.</p>
  </div>
  <div class="friendbot4-initialHide js-friendbot4__navWrapper">
    <nav class="friendbot4__nav">
      <button class="s-button js-friendbot4__nav__prev">Back</button>
      <!-- <a class="friendbot4__nav__minimize js-friendbot4__nav__minimize">minimize</a> -->
      <button class="s-button js-friendbot4__nav__next">Next</button>
    </nav>
  </div>
</div>
